%F A015222 From _Ant King_, Oct 17 2012: (Start)
%F A015222 a(n) = (3 + 4*n - (-1)^n)*(2 + 4*n - (-1)^n)*(1 + 4*n - (-1)^n)/24.
%F A015222 a(n) = 3*a(n-2) - 3*a(n-4) + a(n-6) + 128. (End)
